<HEADLINE>
<P>
NIBBLES AND BITS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Compiled by Ken Williams 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Starting June 4, the Laguna Art Museum will extend its weekend hours.The 
museum will stay open until 9 p.m. on Saturdays and 7 p.m. on Sundays. 
(Tuesdays through Fridays, the museum will close at 5 p.m., as usual.) The 
special hours will continue through Aug. 28. The Newport Harbor Art Museum and 
the Bowers Museum of Cultural Art will not be offering extended summer hours. 
However, Newport Harbor's bookstore will have reduced hours, from 11:30 a.m. to 
4 p.m. 
</P>
