<TEXT>
<P>
 Want to chill out and learn something at the same time? 
</P>
<P>
 Zygon International Inc. of Redmond, Wash., says its Learning Machine uses "a 
breakthrough system that combines entertainment, virtual-reality-like 
experiences and the inducement of altered mind states to create an environment 
optimally conducive to learning." 
</P>
<P>
 That means: Wear digital headphones, listen to special discs, then don a 
"light shield" with flashing lights and special sounds to "imprint" information 
into your memory. 
