<TEXT>
<P>
 Dick Clark Productions Inc., a Burbank producer of television shows, said its 
fiscal third-quarter profit surged to $4.04 million from a profit of $1.14 
million a year ago. 
</P>
<P>
 The earnings for the three months that ended March 31 was the biggest 
