<BYLINE>
<P>
From Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Prosecutors dropped all World Trade Center bombing charges against a Jordanian 
on Monday, admitting they lacked evidence to convict him. He pleaded guilty to 
a lesser count of lying on an immigration form. 
</P>
<P>
 Bilal Alkaisi, 29, will not cooperate with prosecutors under the deal, his 
