Bradley was crossing, but Oggs drove into the parking lane to get by the other 
cars, according to a sheriff's report. Oggs, a Lancaster resident, did not see 
Bradley until her car hit him. The boy was dragged nearly 60 feet by Oggs' car. 
</P>
