<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Beauty pageant -- A story in the April 25 editions of The Times describing a 
dispute over the cancellation of the USA Petite Model Pageant incorrectly 
quoted pageant lawyer Barry Rothman as saying there was no fee schedule 
governing payment to the pageant's producer. In fact, a fee schedule did exist. 
</P>
